				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="dablink">This article is about the American rock band.  For other uses, see <a href="Blondie_(disambiguation)" title="Blondie (disambiguation)" class="mw-redirect">Blondie</a>.</div>
