<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Blondie_(band)&action=edit&section=13.php.html" title="Edit section: Awards and nominations">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Awards_and_nominations">Awards and nominations</span></h2>
