<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Blondie_(band)&action=edit&section=15.php.html" title="Edit section: Notes and references">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Notes_and_references">Notes and references</span></h2>
<div class="reflist references-column-count references-column-count-2" style="-moz-column-count: 2; -webkit-column-count: 2; column-count: 2; list-style-type: decimal;">
<ol class="references">
